Updated Kitchen with a breakfast nook to enjoy the view of this beautiful wooded acreage. Master bedroom and bath with his and hers vanity jetted tub and walk in shower. Huge Deck for summer enjoyment. Comes with an attached over sized 2 car garage with storage newly painted. No work to be done here. Country living close to everything. This one won't last long you better hurry.
